data.description: Presenting this charming 4-bed, 2-bath  3 CAR GARAGE home! Modern interior features an inviting foyer, wood-look flooring, upgraded tall baseboards, and chic light fixtures. Spacious great room highlights sliding glass doors that provide a seamless connection to the back patio, creating an easy flow for indoor-outdoor living. SS appliances, granite counters, subway tile backsplash, walk-in pantry, espresso cabinets w/crown moulding, and an island w/breakfast bar complete this impeccable kitchen. The main bedroom boasts direct access to the back patio and an ensuite with dual sinks and a large walk-in closet. The backyard is a true outdoor oasis, providing a covered patio, artificial turf, and a crystal-clear pool. This one-of-a-kind gem won't last long! LOOK TODAY!
